parameters: Zaida-G Combatant: "Lord Domudora, I have a report!"

Zaida-G Combatant: "It seems that Lord Itoda-G, under Lord Galves, has
been defeated."

Zaida-G Combatant: "Following Lord Spaida-G, once again by Pony-
Celes..."

Strategist Domudora: "Foh foh foh, is that so? That is indeed
delightful."
Strategist Domudora: "I can just picture Galves's frustrated face."

Strategist Domudora: "The end for you will come when you've lost all
your subordinates and are left completely exposed."

Strategist Domudora: "Simple-minded fools like you are a hindrance to
my plans..."
Zaida-G Combatant: "Excuse me, but what do you mean by that?"

Strategist Domudora: "Hmm? Is there any benefit for me in telling you
that?"
Zaida-G Combatant: "That is..."

Zaida-G Combatant: "...I spoke out of mere curiosity. I deeply
apologize for overstepping my bounds."

Strategist Domudora: "It's fine. It's natural to be curious and to
wonder about things."

Strategist Domudora: "However, I cannot disclose that to you.
Because..."
Strategist Domudora: "You are..."
Strategist Domudora: "Galves's dog, after all!!"
Zaida-G Combatant: "What!!"

Strategist Domudora: "Even a fool like you must have had a moment of
clarity. You found my actions in reviving Zaibo-G suspicious."

Strategist Domudora: "Did you really think that I, who bears the name
of strategist, would not notice a spy?"

Zaida-G Combatant: "No... I didn't want to do this, but I was told I'd
be killed if I didn't... I had no choice!"
Strategist Domudora: "I have one question for you."

Strategist Domudora: "Currently, Pony-Celes is interfering with
Zaida-G's plans. Now, who do you think is the incompetent one, that
fool or me?"

Zaida-G Combatant: "Th-that would be, of course, Lord Galves... no,
Galves, Galves is the incompetent one!!"

Strategist Domudora: "Right you are. I... I detest incompetent
creatures."

Strategist Domudora: "Galves, who only has strength as his asset, and
you, an incompetent spy."

Strategist Domudora: "Incompetence is something that makes me nauseous
just by looking at it. So, foh foh foh... please die."
Strategist Domudora: "Come out now. My dear pet."

Zaida-G Combatant: "This is... the Zaibo-G that Lord Galves
mentioned!!"
Zaibo-G: "Did you call for me, Lord Domudora?"

Zaida-G Combatant: "Zaibo-G can speak...!! Why!? This creature is
supposed to be a mindless beast!?"

Strategist Domudora: "Heheheh, with a little modification from me,
such a feat is trivial."

Strategist Domudora: "Now, dispose of this trash! And make sure
nothing is left behind."
Zaibo-G: "Gheheheh, understood..."
Zaida-G Combatant: "G-gaaaahhhhh--!!"

Strategist Domudora: "No one shall interfere with my plans. Foh foh
foh!"
